> > > xfs fails as
> > > 
> > > +mount: /mnt/scratch: wrong fs type, bad option, bad superblock on /dev/mapper/testvg-lv2, missing codepage or helper program, or other error.
> > > +qmount failed
> > > 
> > > and dmesg says
> > > 
